{"id":312395,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-中国选举观察（2013）之二十九-独立竞选/","date":"2013-09-07T02:18:49Z","modified":"2013-09-07T02:18:49Z","title":"维权网 | 中国选举观察（2013）之二十九——独立竞选人李碧云“涉嫌破坏选举罪”一案因遭抗议未能开庭（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员姚立法报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>时许，近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>位关注广东省佛山市顺德区容桂街道容里村、独立竞选区人大代表的初步候选人李碧云“涉嫌破坏选举罪”一案一审宣判的人士，汇集于顺德区法院。据目击者称，这近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>人中，有国内和国外的记者、有江西省九江市的杨崇和湖南省桂阳县的谢文飞、有顺德区及其以外的广东省部分区县的百余农民。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>专程旁听或采访李碧云“涉嫌破坏选举罪”一案一审宣判的上述人士，被顺德区法院拒之门外。法院工作人员对李碧云的说法是，该法院第三审判庭里面已坐满了人，现只留有五个座位可供李碧云的亲属进入法庭旁听，其余所有人不得进入。李碧云和其亲属质疑法院不公开审判没有法律依据。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据现场目击者称，有一黑社会模样的人抢记者的摄像机，被围观的数十人指责哄走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>近十时，百余位准备参加旁听的人士，自发集体举牌抗议顺德法院的做法。他们一手举着开庭传票，另一手举着“抗议”二字。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在一处围观人群里，有两人高举“李碧云何罪之有！独立参选竟被入罪？”的展牌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>十一时许，因李碧云要求法院允许村民旁听未获准，李碧云拒绝进入法院，顺德法院对李碧云“涉嫌破坏选举罪”一案一审宣判未能如期开庭。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>维权网曾对李碧云一案高度关注。独立竞选人李碧云的竞选顾问姚立法认为，李碧云是无罪的；顺德区人大常委会领导的被李碧云“破坏”的选举是非法的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>附：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日李碧云被顺德公安局以＂涉嫌破坏选举罪＂刑事拘留；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日李碧云被顺德公安局以＂涉嫌破坏选举罪＂逮捕；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日李碧云收到顺德检察院起诉书；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日李碧云收到顺德法院延迟审理通知书；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日～</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日顺德法院开庭审理李碧云＂涉嫌破坏选举罪＂一案；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日李碧云＂涉嫌破坏选举罪＂一案补充侦查，审理延迟一个月；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日李碧云收到恢复审理决定书；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日李碧云取保候审；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27 </span><span>日法院宣读李碧云被监视居住证书；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日李碧云被撤销监视居住；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日李碧云收到开庭传票；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日李碧云＂涉嫌破坏选举罪＂一案未如期开庭。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-oA0taJZQ8nY/UiqCZ7GUsMI/AAAAAAAAn4s/GPTLD6JzmtA/s1600/422.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"126\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-oA0taJZQ8nY/UiqCZ7GUsMI/AAAAAAAAn4s/GPTLD6JzmtA/s320/422.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-46f6JBP6PVo/UiqCqQE_zZI/AAAAAAAAn5E/sMHouvE09Ck/s1600/425.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"147\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-46f6JBP6PVo/UiqCqQE_zZI/AAAAAAAAn5E/sMHouvE09Ck/s320/425.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-n5w9bGVOjQI/UiqCg9A5ZsI/AAAAAAAAn48/CwSb2-WJBaw/s1600/415.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"238\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-n5w9bGVOjQI/UiqCg9A5ZsI/AAAAAAAAn48/CwSb2-WJBaw/s320/415.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-XpaCaYu6nrA/UiqCdvzlFII/AAAAAAAAn40/Qogapl3oXuk/s1600/420.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"238\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-XpaCaYu6nrA/UiqCdvzlFII/AAAAAAAAn40/Qogapl3oXuk/s320/420.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}